\id PHP New Alpha - June 11, 2007
\h FILIPENSES
\toc3 Fil
\toc2 Filipenses
\toc1 RI WUJ RI XUTZꞌIBꞌAJ RI PABLO CHIKE RI KOJONELABꞌ AꞌJ FILIPOS
\mt1 RI WUJ RI XUTZꞌIBꞌAJ RI PABLO CHIKE RI KOJONELABꞌ AꞌJ FILIPOS
\imt2 Majibꞌal re
\ip Pa ri ukabꞌ bꞌinem ri Pablo are xeꞌ kukꞌ ri winaq ri man aꞌj Israel taj, ri taqoꞌn Pablo xtobꞌanik rech xmajix jun komontyox pa ri tinimit Filipo. (Chawila pa Hechos 16:11-40.) Filipo jun tinimit jawjeꞌ xeꞌsax wi bꞌik ri ajchꞌoꞌjabꞌ chajil tinimit re Roma. Ri winaq aꞌj Filipo xuꞌx e tobꞌanelabꞌ xuqujeꞌ e rech chꞌabꞌeꞌn ri Pablo kꞌa xkil na ri uchak ri Pablo.
\ip Are xkita ri winaq aꞌj Filipo chi ri Pablo xtzꞌapix pa cheꞌ je laꞌ Roma xkimulij pwaq che tobꞌal re xuqujeꞌ xkitaq bꞌik jun kachiꞌl rukꞌ ubꞌiꞌnam Epafrodito.
\ip Are ikꞌowinaq chi jun janipa qꞌotaj ri Pablo xutaq bꞌik jun wuj jawjeꞌ xutyoxij wi bꞌik ri kitobꞌanik xuqujeꞌ ri achiꞌlanem ri xkiya che.
\ip Ri Pablo retaꞌm chi ri aꞌj Filipos tajin kakiriq nim kꞌaxal, rumal riꞌ kukoj ri ukꞌaslemal che jun kꞌambꞌejabꞌal noꞌj xuqujeꞌ rajawaxik chi jun kakiꞌkotik pune kꞌo pa kꞌaxkꞌolal.
\ip Ri Pablo rukꞌ chuqꞌabꞌ kubꞌij pa ri nimalaj ja jawjeꞌ kꞌo wi ri César chi are chi are ri Jesús Ajawxel. Ri urayibꞌal ukꞌuꞌx are chi konojel ri aꞌj Filipos kakitzijoj ri utz laj tzij man rukꞌ ta xibꞌin ibꞌ.
\ip Rukꞌ jun jeꞌl laj bꞌix, ri Pablo kuꞌtaqchiꞌj ri aꞌj Filipos rech kepatanijik jetaq ri xubꞌan ri Jesús, ri Jesús man xunaꞌ ta nimal chi are Dios xumochꞌ ribꞌ kꞌa pa ri kamikal xa rumal ke nikꞌaj chik. Are wa ri rajawaxik kubꞌan ri winaq pa ri rajawarem ri Dios.
\ip Ri qachoch kꞌo pa ri ajawarem re ri Dios rumal riꞌ qayeꞌm ri utzalijibꞌal ri Qakolonel rukꞌ ronojel qanimaꞌ.
\ip Ri Jesús riꞌ kukꞌex na bꞌik ri qatyoꞌjal kubꞌan che jetaq ri re areꞌ are xkꞌastaj chikixoꞌl ri kaminaqibꞌ.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Ri Pablo rachiꞌl ri Timoteo e patanil rech ri Cristo, kakitaq rutzil kiwach konojel ri e tyoxalaj taq winaq ri e kꞌo pa Cristo je laꞌ pa ri tinimit Filipos, kukꞌ ri e kꞌamal taq bꞌe xuqujeꞌ ri e patanijelabꞌ.
\v 2 Toqꞌobꞌ xuqujeꞌ jaꞌmaril chiꞌwe rech ri Dios Tataxel xuqujeꞌ rech ri Ajawxel Jesucristo.
\s1 Chꞌawem xuqujeꞌ tyoxinik
\p 
\v 3 Kintyoxin che ri Dios are kixnaꞌtaj chwe.
\v 4 Kinbꞌan chꞌawem pa iwiꞌ rukꞌ kiꞌkotemal.
\v 5 Jeriꞌ rumal ixkꞌolinaq loq pa ri utz laj utzij ri Dios xchapleꞌtaj loq are xixkojonik kꞌa pa taq we qꞌij kamik riꞌ.
\v 6 Qas uchapom na kꞌuꞌx chi ri majininaq loq ri utz laj chak pa iwanimaꞌ, kutzꞌaqatisaj na kꞌa pa ri qꞌij rech ri upetibꞌal ri Jesucristo.
\v 7 Sibꞌalaj utz we jeriꞌ kinchoman in chiꞌwe, jeriꞌ rumal ix kꞌo pa wanimaꞌ xuqujeꞌ kixnaꞌtaj chwe are in kꞌo pa cheꞌ xuqujeꞌ are in kꞌo chikiwach ri qꞌatal taq tzij chuqꞌalajisaxik ri utz laj tzij, iwonojel kꞌo iwe che ri utoqꞌobꞌ ri Dios ri uyaꞌom chwe.
\v 8 Rumal cher karil ri Dios chi sibꞌalaj ixnuloqꞌ rukꞌ ri uloqꞌanik ri Cristo Jesús xuqujeꞌ kixinbꞌisoj.
\v 9 Kinta kꞌu pa ri nuchꞌawem chi ri iloqꞌanik, kanimar na pa etaꞌmabꞌal xuqujeꞌ pa noꞌjibꞌal.
\v 10 Rech jeriꞌ are kichaꞌ ri sibꞌalaj utz ubꞌanik, xuqujeꞌ kixux chꞌajchꞌoj, man kꞌo ta imak pa ri upetibꞌal ri Cristo.
\v 11 Xuqujeꞌ rech ixnojinaq chubꞌanik ri utzilal rech jeriꞌ kiya unimal uqꞌij xuqujeꞌ bꞌixonem che ri Dios.
\s1 Ri kꞌaslemal pa Cristo
\p 
\v 12 Qachalal, kawaj kiwetaꞌmaj chi ronojel ri xkꞌulmataj wukꞌ xubꞌano chi xnimar utzijoxik ri utz laj tzij.
\v 13 Qas xqꞌalajinik chikiwach ri e chajil taq rech ri nimalaj ja rech ri qꞌatal tzij xuqujeꞌ chikiwach konojel chi xinkoj pa cheꞌ xa rumal rech ri Cristo.
\v 14 Tyox chi xintzꞌapiꞌk pa cheꞌ, sibꞌalaj e kꞌi chike ri alaxik ri jeqel kikꞌuꞌx che ri Ajawxel, xkichapleꞌj utzijoxik ri utzij ri Dios man rukꞌ ta xibꞌin ibꞌ.
\p 
\v 15 E kꞌo jujun kakitzijoj ri Cristo rumal cher kꞌax kakinaꞌ chaqe, e kꞌo chi nikꞌaj xa rumal sibꞌalaj utz kanimaꞌ.
\v 16 Ri kꞌisbꞌal wok kakitzijoj ri Cristo rumal cher kinkiloqꞌaj, rumal cher ketaꞌm chi in in chaꞌtal apanoq chuqꞌalajisaxik ri utz laj taq tzij.
\v 17 Ri kakitzijoj ri Cristo rumal cher kꞌax kakinaꞌ chwe, man qas ta rukꞌ rutzil kanimaꞌ kakibꞌano, are kakaj katzꞌaqatisax ri kꞌax chwij pa cheꞌ.
\v 18 ¿Jas kꞌu kaqabꞌij? Jas ta bꞌa lo rumal tajin katzijox ri Cristo we kꞌu qas rukꞌ chꞌajchꞌoj animaꞌaj o man rukꞌ ta neꞌ, are waꞌ kayoꞌw nukiꞌkotemal in. Jeꞌ, kinkiꞌkot na rumal rech.
\v 19 Rumal cher wetaꞌm chi ri ichꞌawem xuqujeꞌ ri utobꞌanik ri Uxlabꞌixel rech ri Cristo, are kinesan na bꞌi waral.
\v 20 Ri kurayij na kꞌuꞌx are chi man kel ta nukꞌixibꞌal, xane rukꞌ ronojel kuꞌlibꞌal kꞌuꞌx we kinkamik o kinkꞌasiꞌk, kayaꞌtaj na uqꞌij ri Cristo pa ri nutyoꞌjal.
\v 21 Rumal cher chwe in ri kꞌaslem are Cristo, ri kamikal chꞌekoj riꞌ.
\v 22 We xaq jeꞌ kinkꞌasiꞌ na cho we uwachulew, xa kꞌa kꞌo na kintayij riꞌ che ri Dios, man kinriq ta kꞌut jachin chike kinchaꞌo.
\v 23 Ukobꞌchal we jastaq riꞌ utz chwe, kawaj kineꞌek rukꞌ ri Cristo rumal sibꞌalaj jeꞌlik ri kꞌolem rukꞌ.
\v 24 Xa kꞌu rumal iwe kinkanaj na kanoq cho ri uwachulew.
\v 25 Qas uchapom na kꞌuꞌx, wetaꞌm chi kinkꞌojiꞌ na iwukꞌ rech jeriꞌ kintobꞌan rukꞌ ri ikiꞌkotemal xuqujeꞌ pa ri ikojobꞌal.
\v 26 Rech jeriꞌ ri ikiꞌkotemal pa Cristo kanimar na rumal we, are kiwil chinuwach junmul.
\p 
\v 27 Xaq xwi kinchilibꞌej chiꞌwe je chixnoꞌjinoq jetaq ri kubꞌij ri utz laj tzij rech ri Cristo, rech pune in kꞌo iwukꞌ o man in kꞌo ta neꞌ, katataj na chi ko ix kꞌolik pa ri uxlabꞌal tajin kikoj ichuqꞌabꞌ pa ri kojobꞌal chutzijoxik ri utz laj tzij.
\v 28 Makixiꞌj ta iwibꞌ chike ri kakibꞌan kikꞌulel chiꞌwe, rumal cher ri utz laj tzij kubꞌan na chi kasach kiwach we winaq riꞌ, are kꞌu chiꞌwe ix ri utz laj tzij are jun kꞌutbꞌal re ri kolotajem ri kape rukꞌ ri Dios.
\v 29 Rumal cher ri ix man xwi ta yaꞌtal bꞌe chiꞌwe kixkojon che ri Cristo, xane kiriq xuqujeꞌ kꞌax rumal rech.
\v 30 Rumal tajin kikoj ichuqꞌabꞌ chubꞌanik ri chꞌoꞌj ri xiwilo xinbꞌan ojer xuqujeꞌ tajin kinbꞌan kamik riꞌ.
\c 2
\s1 Chiwesaj uwach ri Cristo
\p 
\v 1 We ri Cristo uyaꞌom ichuqꞌabꞌ rech kiꞌtaqchiꞌj nikꞌaj chik, xuqujeꞌ we ri iloqꞌanik kixutaqchiꞌj chukubꞌisaxik kikꞌuꞌx nikꞌaj chik, xuqujeꞌ we iwonojel xa jun Uxlabꞌal ixukꞌaꞌninaq xuqujeꞌ we kel ikꞌuꞌx chike nikꞌaj chik,
\v 2 chininojisaj che kiꞌkotemal, chijunamaj ikꞌuꞌx, chijunamaj ri iloqꞌanik, xuqujeꞌ chijunamaj ri iwanimaꞌ xuqujeꞌ ri ichomabꞌal.
\v 3 Mibꞌan jun jastaq rukꞌ nimal o xa rumal kiwaj kitzukuj chꞌoꞌj, xane chibꞌana rukꞌ mochꞌochꞌem, chiꞌwilaꞌ chi are e nimaꞌq ri nikꞌaj chik chiꞌwach.
\v 4 Man xwi ta kiwilij ri jastaq ri kajawataj chiꞌwe ix pa ijujunal, xane chiwila xuqujeꞌ ri kirajawaxik ri nikꞌaj chik.
\p 
\v 5 Ri inoꞌjibꞌal rajawaxik je kuxik jetaq ri rech ri Cristo Jesús,
\v 6 ri areꞌ, pune are Dios, man xukoj ta uchuqꞌabꞌ chubꞌixik chi tzi are wi Dios.
\v 7 Xane xubꞌan nitzꞌ chibꞌil ribꞌ jeꞌ jas jun ajchak, xalax pa ri uwachulew jetaq jun winaq, xuqujeꞌ xubꞌan achi chibꞌil ribꞌ.
\v 8 Are xubꞌan achi chibꞌil ribꞌ, xumochꞌ ribꞌ, xnimanik xeꞌ kꞌa pa ri kamikal, kamikal cho ri ripbꞌal.
\v 9 Rumal riꞌ, ri Dios xuya nimalaj uqꞌij, xuya ri bꞌiꞌaj che puꞌwiꞌ ronojel bꞌiꞌaj.
\v 10 Rech jeriꞌ kakimej kichꞌek choch konojel ri e kꞌo pa ri kaj, ri e kꞌo choch ri uwachulew xuqujeꞌ ri e kꞌo chuxeꞌ ri uwachulew.
\v 11 Xuqujeꞌ rech konojel kakiqꞌalajisaj rukꞌ ri kichiꞌ chi are ri Jesucristo Ajawxel rech jeriꞌ kayaꞌtaj uqꞌij ri Dios Tataxel.
\s1 Ri qꞌalajisanik ri kabꞌan pa ri tunal ri katunanik
\p 
\v 12 Xaq jeriꞌ, loqꞌalaj taq qachalal, rumal cher amaqꞌel kixniman chwe, man xwi ta are in kꞌo iwukꞌ, xane are man in kꞌo ta iwukꞌ, chiwukꞌaj ri ikolotajem rukꞌ mochꞌoj ibꞌ xuqujeꞌ rukꞌ nimanik.
\v 13 Jeriꞌ rumal cher are ri Dios kabꞌanow chiꞌwe chi kixnimanik xuqujeꞌ kiwaj kibꞌan ronojel ri jastaq rech kibꞌano ri urayibꞌal ukꞌuꞌx.
\p 
\v 14 Chibꞌana ri jastaq man rukꞌ ta chꞌaoj ibꞌ xuqujeꞌ man rukꞌ ta oyawal.
\v 15 Jeriꞌ qas ixchꞌajchꞌoj man kꞌo ta imak, rumal cher ix, ix ralkꞌwaꞌl ri Dios, ri ix kꞌo chikixoꞌl ri winaq ri aꞌjmakibꞌ, ri man kꞌyaqal taj kechomanik. Ix kꞌo chikixoꞌl we winaq riꞌ, jetaq ri chꞌumil ri kachuplinik cho ri kaj.
\v 16 Are chiwilij uqꞌalajisaxik ri tzij rech kꞌaslemal. Rech jeriꞌ are kuriq ri upetibꞌal ri Cristo, kakiꞌkot na kꞌuꞌx are kinwetaꞌmaj chi man xaq ta xintzaq ri nuchuqꞌabꞌ, xuqujeꞌ man xaq ta xinchakun chi jeriꞌ.
\v 17 Pune kesax na ri nukꞌaslemal xuqujeꞌ katzuj na jetaq jun sipanik xa rumal ri ikojobꞌal, kinkiꞌkotik na riꞌ xuqujeꞌ kawaj chi kixkiꞌkot na ix wukꞌ.
\v 18 Ix xuqujeꞌ, chixkiꞌkotoq, xuqujeꞌ chiya we ri ikiꞌkotemal.
\s1 Ri e kebꞌ tobꞌanelabꞌ
\p 
\v 19 Kinwayeꞌj che ri Ajawxel Jesús kinkwinik kintaq bꞌik ri Timoteo iwukꞌ rech jeriꞌ kinkꞌamawaꞌj nuchuqꞌabꞌ are kinwetaꞌmaj jas jeꞌ ibꞌanom.
\v 20 Ri Timoteo sibꞌalaj kꞌax ukꞌuꞌx chiꞌwe, rumal cher kixuloqꞌaj jetaq ri kinbꞌan in.
\v 21 Konojel ri nikꞌaj xaq are kakilij ri jastaq ri kajawataj chike, man are ta kakilij ri karaj ri Jesucristo.
\v 22 Ix iwetaꞌm uwach ri Timoteo, sibꞌalaj utz ri kanoꞌjinik, ubꞌanom ri patanijik wukꞌ chuqꞌalajisaxik ri utz laj tzij, je ri kꞌo jun alkꞌwaꞌlaxel ri sibꞌalaj utz kanoꞌjinik che ri utat.
\v 23 Kawaj kꞌut kintaq bꞌik aninaq iwukꞌ, xwi wayeꞌm kinwetaꞌmaj jas kakꞌulmataj wukꞌ.
\v 24 Kuꞌl na kꞌuꞌx chirij ri Ajawxel chi kineꞌ xuqujeꞌ na in, kixeꞌnwilaꞌ.
\p 
\v 25 Xuqujeꞌ xinchomaj chi utz kubꞌan chiꞌwe we kintaq bꞌik ri Epafrodito iwukꞌ, areꞌ jun alaxik xuqujeꞌ jun tobꞌanel, wachiꞌl pa taq ri nuchꞌoꞌj, are waꞌ ri xitaq loq chinupatanixik.
\v 26 Ri Epafrodito sibꞌalaj kixubꞌisoj xuqujeꞌ kꞌax ranimaꞌ chiꞌwe xiwetaꞌmaj waꞌ chi yawabꞌ.
\v 27 Qas ne tzij wi xyawajik, jubꞌiqꞌ xraj xkamik. Ri Dios kꞌut xel ukꞌuꞌx che, man xwi taj xel ukꞌuꞌx che areꞌ xane xel xuqujeꞌ ukꞌuꞌx chwe in, rech jeriꞌ man xnimataj ta ri nubꞌis.
\v 28 Rumal riꞌ kintaq chi bꞌi iwukꞌ rech kixkiꞌkot chi junmul we chiwil uwach, rech xuqujeꞌ man kakꞌaxir ta chi wanimaꞌ in.
\v 29 Chikꞌamawaꞌj pa ri Ajawxel, rukꞌ kiꞌkotemal xuqujeꞌ nim chiꞌwila ri je kenoꞌjinik jetaq ri areꞌ.
\v 30 Jeriꞌ rumal jubꞌiqꞌ xraj xkamik rumal ri uchak ri Cristo, xuya ri ukꞌaslemal rech xubꞌan ri patanijik ri man xixkwin ta ix xibꞌano.
\c 3
\s1 Ri kuꞌlibꞌal qakꞌuꞌx pa Cristo
\p 
\v 1 Xaq kꞌu jeriꞌ wachalal, chixkiꞌkot pa ri Ajawxel. Man kinqꞌiꞌtaj taj kintzalij utzꞌibꞌaxik we jastaq riꞌ chiꞌwe xuqujeꞌ wetaꞌm chi utz kubꞌan chiꞌwe ix.
\v 2 Chichajij iwibꞌ chike ri itzel taq winaq ri jer kenoꞌjin tzꞌiꞌ, ri aꞌreꞌ kakaj kakoj iwetal.
\v 3 Jeriꞌ rumal ri uj ri uj kojom qetal, kaqapatanij ri Dios pa ri uxlabꞌal xuqujeꞌ man kakubꞌiꞌ ta qakꞌuꞌx pa ri qatyoꞌjal xane nim kaqanaꞌo rumal uj kꞌo pa Cristo Jesús.
\v 4 Ri in qas kuꞌlinaq na kꞌuꞌx chirij waꞌ we riꞌ. We kꞌo jun kukojo chi kꞌo rumal kakubꞌiꞌ ukꞌuꞌx chirij ri uchuqꞌabꞌ ri winaq, in in kꞌo na cho we winaq riꞌ.
\v 5 Kojtal wetal chi wuq qꞌij, in aj pa ri tinimit Israel, in rijaꞌl ri Benjamín, qas in hebreo wi, xuqujeꞌ chutereneꞌxik ri taqanik xinkꞌojiꞌk kukꞌ ri fariseos.
\v 6 Qas uchapom wi na kꞌuꞌx chupatanixik ri taqanik, rumal riꞌ xinbꞌan kꞌax chike ri komontyox. Man kꞌo ta jun kabꞌin chwe chi mat xinnimaj ri taqanik.
\v 7 Pune jeriꞌ, ronojel ri chꞌekoj kanoq chinuwach nabꞌe, chanim kinchomaj chi man kꞌo ta kutayij chwe rumal cher are nim na ri xubꞌan ri Cristo choch ronojel.
\v 8 Qas ne tzij wi, man kꞌo ta kutayij ronojel ri xinbꞌan kanoq rumal chi are sibꞌalaj nim na uqꞌij ri retaꞌmaxik uwach ri wAjaw Cristo Jesús cho we jastaq riꞌ.
\v 9 Rech jeriꞌ kinbꞌan na riqoj ibꞌ rukꞌ areꞌ. Man are ta kawaj kinbꞌan ri sukꞌal re ri taqanik, xane are kawaj ri sukꞌal ri kape che ri Dios pa ri kojobꞌal.
\v 10 Ronojel xintzaq kanoq rumal retaꞌmaxik uwach ri Cristo, xuqujeꞌ rech kinnaꞌo ri ukwinem ri xukꞌutu are xkꞌastajik chikixoꞌl ri kaminaqibꞌ, rech xuqujeꞌ kinriq we ri kꞌax rukꞌ Areꞌ rech jeriꞌ xuqujeꞌ kinkamik jetaq ri xubꞌan Areꞌ.
\v 11 Kurayij na kꞌuꞌx kinukꞌastajisaj na ri Dios chikixoꞌl ri kaminaqibꞌ.
\s1 Winaq ajchikaj
\p 
\v 12 Man tajin ta kinbꞌij chi xchꞌektaj wumal ronojel, o man kꞌo ta chi kajawataj chwe. Xane xaq jeꞌ inbꞌenaq, kurayij ri wanimaꞌ kinopanik chubꞌanik ri inusikꞌim wi apanoq ri Cristo.
\v 13 Wachalal, wetaꞌm chi kꞌamajaꞌ kinopanik jawjeꞌ ri yaꞌtalik kinopan wi. Xwi ri kinbꞌano are chi kasachan kanoq chwe ri xikꞌow kanoq, are kinkoj nuchuqꞌabꞌ chubꞌanik ri kꞌo apanoq chinuwach.
\v 14 Xaq jeriꞌ inbꞌenaq chinuwach rech kinopanik jawjeꞌ ri yaꞌtal wi kinopanik rech jeriꞌ keꞌnriqa na ri utzujum ri Dios chwe pa ri sikꞌinik rech chikajil pa Cristo Jesús.
\p 
\v 15 Xaq jeriꞌ qonojel ri uj tzꞌaqat chik kaqanaꞌo, xa jun chujchomanoq, we kꞌu jun chi wi kixchomanik, ri Dios riꞌ kuqꞌalajisaj chiꞌwach.
\v 16 Junam qabꞌana che ri qachomabꞌal japawjeꞌ ri ujopaninaq wi chanim.
\p 
\v 17 Wachalal, are chiwesaj uwach ri kinbꞌano, xuqujeꞌ chiꞌwila ri je tajin kenoꞌjinik jetaq ri qakꞌutum chikiwach.
\v 18 Jetaq ri nubꞌim chiꞌwe, kinkamulij chi ubꞌixik junmul rukꞌ uwaꞌl nubꞌoqꞌoch, sibꞌalaj e kꞌi ri kakichomaj chi man kꞌo ta kutayij chike ri ukamikal ri Cristo cho ri ripbꞌal.
\v 19 Kakꞌis na tzij pa kiwiꞌ we winaq riꞌ, rumal che ri are kakiqꞌijilaꞌj ri urayibꞌal taq kikꞌuꞌx xuqujeꞌ nimal kakinaꞌo are kakibꞌano ri kꞌixibꞌal ubꞌanik, xaq xwi kakichomaj rij ri jastaq rech uwachulew.
\v 20 Ri uj kꞌut, uj rech pa ri kaj, qayeꞌm apanoq ri Kolonel, ri Ajawxel Jesucristo ri upetik chilaꞌ chikaj.
\v 21 Ri Jesucristo rukꞌ ronojel ri ukwinem ri ukojom chuchajixik ronojel ri utikom, are kakꞌexow na bꞌik ri qatyoꞌjal ri xaq kaqꞌayik, pa tyoꞌjal ri kajuluwik, jetaq ri rech Areꞌ.
\c 4
\s1 Chixkiꞌkotoq pa ri Ajawxel Jesús
\p 
\v 1 Xaq jeriꞌ, loqꞌalaj taq wachalal, sibꞌalaj ixnuloqꞌ xuqujeꞌ sibꞌalaj nimal kinnaꞌ rumal iwe. Ko chixkꞌoloq pa ri Ajawxel.
\p 
\v 2 Kinta jun toqꞌobꞌ che ri Evodia xuqujeꞌ ri Síntique rech kakijunamaj ri kichomanik pa ri Ajawxel.
\v 3 Kinta xuqujeꞌ jun toqꞌobꞌ chawe at sukꞌalaj wachiꞌl, kawaj kinta chawe chi kabꞌan jun toqꞌobꞌ chikitoꞌik we ixoqibꞌ riꞌ, aꞌreꞌ echakuninaq wukꞌ chutzijoxik ri utz laj tzij, xuqujeꞌ ri Clemente rachiꞌl ri nikꞌaj taq tobꞌanelabꞌ chik ri tzꞌibꞌatal ri kibꞌiꞌ pa ri wuj rech kꞌaslemal.
\p 
\v 4 Amaqꞌel chixkiꞌkotoq pa ri Ajawxel, junmul chik kinbꞌij: Chixkiꞌkotoq.
\v 5 Chibꞌana ri utzilal rech konojel ri winaq kakilo ri kibꞌano. Man naj ta chik kꞌo wi loq ri upetibꞌal ri Ajawxel.
\p 
\v 6 Makꞌaxir iwanimaꞌ che ri jastaq, xane chibꞌana chꞌawem ronojel mul, chibꞌij che ri Dios jas jeꞌ ri kiwaj, xuqujeꞌ kixtyoxinoq che ronojel ri ubꞌanom.
\v 7 Rech jeriꞌ kuya na ri Dios ri ujaꞌmaril chiꞌwe, are waꞌ ri jaꞌmaril ri man kekwin taj ri winaq cho ri uwachulew kakichꞌobꞌ rij, are waꞌ ri katoꞌw ri kanimaꞌ xuqujeꞌ ri kichomabꞌal ri e rech chik ri Cristo.
\p 
\v 8 Kꞌisbꞌal rech Qachalal, qas chixchomanoq chirij ronojel ri qas tzij, ronojel ri qas utz kanimaxik, ronojel ri sukꞌ, ronojel ri chꞌajchꞌoj, ronojel ri qas kajoror ubꞌanik, ronojel ri kuyak mayijanik xuqujeꞌ ri yaꞌtalik kaya uqꞌij.
\p 
\v 9 Are chibꞌana ri xiwetaꞌmaj, xito, xiwilo, xuqujeꞌ xikꞌamawaꞌj chwe in, rech jeriꞌ ri Dios rech jaꞌmaril kakꞌojiꞌ iwukꞌ.
\s1 Ri Pablo katyoxin che ri tobꞌanik ri xukꞌamawaꞌj
\p 
\v 10 Sibꞌalaj kinkiꞌkotik pa ri Ajawxel rumal junmul chik xixchoman chwe. Qas wetaꞌm wi chi kiwaj kixtobꞌanik xa man iriqom taj jun qꞌijal chuyaꞌik ri itobꞌanik.
\v 11 Man tajin ta kinbꞌij waꞌ chiꞌwe xa rumal kꞌo nurajawaxik, ri in rumal wetaꞌm kakubꞌiꞌ na kꞌuꞌx rukꞌ ri kꞌo wukꞌ.
\v 12 Wetaꞌm kinkꞌasiꞌk are man kꞌo ta sibꞌalaj kꞌi nujastaq xuqujeꞌ wetaꞌm kinkꞌasiꞌk are kꞌo ronojel wukꞌ. Wetaꞌmam kinkꞌasiꞌk are kꞌo ri kintijo xuqujeꞌ are kinnaꞌ wiꞌjal, we xaq kapulin chi ri kꞌo wukꞌ o man kꞌo ta chi ne ri kinkojo.
\v 13 Ronojel kinkwinik kibꞌano pa Cristo rumal cher Areꞌ kayoꞌw nuchuqꞌabꞌ.
\v 14 Sibꞌalaj utz xixnoꞌjinik are kixkꞌojiꞌ wukꞌ pa ri kꞌax ri xinriqo.
\p 
\v 15 Ri ix ri kixel pa Filipos iwetaꞌm chi pa ri majibꞌal rech ri utzijoxik ri utz laj tzij, are xinel loq pa Macedonia, man kꞌo ta chi jun komontyox xuya pwaq chinutoꞌik, xaq xwi ri ix.
\v 16 Xuqujeꞌ are xinkꞌojiꞌ pa ri tinimit Tesalónica, man xa ta junmul xitaq bꞌik ri itobꞌanik chwe, ri itobꞌanik xinkojo che ri kajawataj chwe.
\v 17 Man tajin ta kinbꞌij waꞌ chiꞌwe rumal kajawataj ri isipanik chwe, xane are kawaj chi ri Dios karil ri kibꞌano.
\v 18 Nukꞌamawaꞌm chik ronojel ri kajawataj chwe, xuqujeꞌ kꞌa nim na kꞌo wukꞌ. Jeriꞌ rumal ri Epafrodito xuya chwe ri xitaq loq rukꞌ. Sibꞌalaj jun kꞌokꞌalaj sipanik ri xitaq loq rukꞌ, are waꞌ ri qas kaqaj cho ri Dios.
\v 19 Are ri nuDios pa ri uqꞌinomal chuya na chiꞌwe ri kajawataj chiꞌwe pa Cristo Jesús.
\v 20 Che ri qaDios xuqujeꞌ Tataxel yaꞌtal wi ri juluwem chibꞌe qꞌij saq. Jeriꞌ.
\s1 Kꞌisbꞌal rutzil wach
\p 
\v 21 Chiya rutzil kiwach konojel ri e tyoxalaj taq winaq pa Cristo Jesús. Kakitaq xuqujeꞌ rutzil iwach ri alaxik ri e kꞌo wukꞌ.
\v 22 Chikꞌamawaꞌj rutzil iwach chike konojel ri e tyoxalaj taq winaq ri e kꞌo wukꞌ, je xuqujeꞌ chike ri e rajchakibꞌ ri nim laj taqanel ri kel pa Roma.
\p 
\v 23 Are ri utoqꞌobꞌ ri Ajawxel Jesucristo, kakanaj kanoq pa ri iwanimaꞌ. Jeriꞌ.
